TopicTitle: KSO Shuttle Missions: STS 106: Bringin A Kerbal Back From the Mun

Articles.Content:
The Sixth of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions and Second Flight of the Tenacious! STS 106's objectives are to return Jeb and his craft from the Mun to Low Kerbin Orbit, rendezvous with KSO Tenacious, and return to the KSC Runway!

Most of the footage is shown in 4x speed for quick viewing.

STS 107 Will launch a scout probe destined for the red planet Duna!

Get the mods!
